{"tid":2250682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港島東仆街了！67樓Neo Derm有超級傳播者","createTime":"2020-10-20T09:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T15:51:50.000Z","uid":355006,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8013c26060102368578e654ed8e3e3580e706ccd","tid":2250682,"uid":355006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:24:12.000Z","msg":"成層67樓仲返緊工，大家睇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n該宗本地個案經油麻地臨時檢測中心發現，為1名32歲女子，與家人居於西灣河嘉亨灣1座，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">於港島東中心任文職工作</span></span>。她於10月16日開始發冷發熱，18日到筲箕灣愛蝶灣商場一名姓鍾的私家醫生診所求醫，醫生當時覺得她「不是太似新冠肺炎」，但如覺得擔心亦建議她做檢測，她於同日到油麻地臨時檢測中心檢測，結果呈陽性。<br />\n張指，患者的同住、曾於傳染期與其食飯的5、6名家人，以及2、3位坐得近的公司同事都須要檢疫，而該公司其餘約100名同層職員則須檢測，公司亦須停業及大清洗。<br />\n消息指，該名確診者病毒含量特高，在檢測前已有輕微病徵，而且病毒量高，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">有機會是超級傳播者</span></span></span>。"},{"pid":"718288161c48a713b0777cb7472437c0761b2eee","tid":2250682,"uid":219583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:27:28.000Z","msg":"呢間野仲成日叫其他分店員工上去開會<br />\n仲要十幾廿人係到玩埋d on9 game<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6515e4057104f5dd2625dea8b23f467b1b5c1d8b","tid":2250682,"uid":94281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:33:09.000Z","msg":"講到個咩cell armour咁巴閉<br />\n叫咗嗰個同事食未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fb7f952d8c0f6a0154fc7bbd4e5dc5f2fe0d1d","tid":2250682,"uid":374180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:40:25.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd610926ed20c19923d0bf9e0e95d67b28562fc","tid":2250682,"uid":14653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10